==Personal life==
He married in 1966 in [[Buckinghamshire]], meeting his wife, [[Chloe Ashcroft]], at the National Theatre. They live in [[Whiteshill, Gloucestershire|Whiteshill and Ruscombe]] in [[Gloucestershire]] and have a son (born 1968) and daughter (born April 1971). He likes to make his own cheese and wine.

